These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, epic, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, rock, country, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, indian, japanese, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, helicopter, snowmobile
1. the indian is the fan of ambient##1
2. the japanese is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the indian is the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left of the thai##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching epic movies##1
7. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the thai is on the far right##1
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | horror   | documentary  | epic  |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | ambient    | pop      | country    |
| Nationality   | german | indian | japanese | thai |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | train       | ship    | helicopter     |

