.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, photography, rock-climbing, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, family, thriller, musical
4 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, biathlon, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the turtle is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person watching musical movies is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's sport is sailing##2
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person watching musical movies and the owner of the turtle##2
7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | photography    | rock-climbing  | baking    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | family  | musical  | thriller |
| Pet           | turtle      | hamster       | chinchilla      | horse       |
| Sport         | rugby    | snowboarding | biathlon | sailing |

