.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, cucumber, grapefruit, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, dancing, card-games, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, social-worker, police-officer, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, van, jet-ski, ship
1. the police-officer is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the doctor##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is reading##1
7. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person eating lettuce is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is reading##2
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person eating grapefruit and the social-worker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | cucumber | grapefruit     | lettuce   | cauliflower     |
| Hobby       | dancing   | baking   | card-games | reading |
| Job         | coach   | police-officer | doctor       | social-worker    |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | van | quad-bike  | ship    |

