.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, doctor, designer, engineer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, sports, horror, satire
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, handball, lacrosse, golf
 1. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is the accountant##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is the designer##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the doctor is between the owner of the hedgehog and the engineer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | accountant  | engineer | doctor     | designer |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | spy  | horror | sports       |
| Pet           | chinchilla       | goldfish    | ferret      | hedgehog           |
| Sport         | basketball | handball   | golf   | lacrosse         |

