.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, tomato, cherry, avocado
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, analyst, photographer, project-manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, spy, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, handball, tennis, biathlon
