 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
 3. the photographer is the person eating tomato##1
 4. the photographer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 8. the analyst is the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person eating cherry is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person watching animation movies##2
10. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | tomato         | cherry         | grapefruit     | avocado      |
