.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, designer, firefighter, photographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, german, pakistani, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting, swimming
1. the fan of gospel is between the person who's sport is swimming and the fan of rock##2
2. the designer is between the fan of gospel and the french##2
3. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the german##2
4. the firefighter is on the left of the german##1
5. the pakistani is the pakistani##1
6. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the german is on the left of the pilot##1
8. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
9. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | firefighter | designer | pilot  | photographer |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | blues       | gospel     | rock      |
| Nationality   | french   | german      | pakistani   | japanese   |
| Sport         | weightlifting   | swimming    | baseball | water-polo   |

