 4. the fan of jazz is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the pakistani is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the japanese is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | crime | musical  | thriller  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | jazz   | classical | disco    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | japanese   | indonesian | polish |
