.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, almond-milk, 7up
There 4 different types of food: peas, lettuce, cranberry, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, baking, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: pony, goat, mouse, rabbit
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person eating peas is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is between the person eating peas and the person eating cranberry##2
 9. the person eating potato is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person eating peas and the person eating cranberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | coffee    | almond-milk    | 7up      | tea |
| Food       | peas        | potato       | cranberry       | lettuce     |
| Hobby      | baking | cooking | rock-climbing | fishing        |
| Pet        | goat       | rabbit     | mouse         | pony           |

