4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, lizard, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, swimming, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, roller, helicopter, car
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the ferret##2
 6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating plum##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | zucchini  | plum | lime     | lemon     |
| Pet         | ferret | fish | dog     | lizard |
| Sport       | cycling  | rugby   | cricket | swimming    |
| Transport   | helicopter   | roller   | bike  | car        |

